title: [Maelstrom Bay, Surface]
description: The green waters of Maelstrom Bay stretch out in all directions.  Low, gentle swells roll in rhythmically from the great western sea.  To the east, the mainland is marked by a sheer, rocky cliff.  The green swells reflect the moonlight, making them shine strangely as they roll in.

paths: Obvious paths: north, northeast, east, southeast, south, west, northwest, down
